high_descs: Turn left and walk around the kitchen island to the counter to the right of the oven.
Pick up the metal pan off of the counter.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the metal pan inside on a shelf and close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the now chilled metal pan then close the fridge.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the sink.
Put the chilled metal pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled metal pan in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the counter top just past the oven, to the left.
Pick up the fry pan under the tomato, on the counter.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator across from you.
Place the fry pan on the second shelf of the refrigerator, wait a moment for the fry pan to chill, then remove the fry pan from the refrigerator.
Turn to your left and go to the sink across from you.
Place the fry pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold fry pan in the sink.

high_descs: turn to the left and take a step and turn to the left and take a step and turn to the right and go to the counter and turn to the left
pick up the grey pan underneath the tomato from the counter tip
turn to the left and take a few steps and turn to the left and go to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door and put the pan on the second shelf and close the door and wait and open the door and take out the pan and close the door
turn to the left twice and take a few steps and turn to the right and go to the sink
put the pan in the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a cold pan in the sink
